        (8, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '[등교하는 토비] 이야기 완료!
기념 사진을 찍어보아요!', '', 'CLEAR', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/voice/school/story01/08.mp3', 1),
        (9, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '오늘은 병원에 가는 날이에요.', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/image/hospital/story01/001.png', 'NORMAL', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/voice/hospital/story01/01.mp3', 2),
        (10, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '병원에 가기전에 옷을 입어야해요.
