        (14, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '토비와 코끼리 친구 코코가 케이크를 먹고 있어요.', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/image/hospital/story01/006.png', 'NORMAL', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/voice/hospital/story01/06.mp3', 2),
        (15, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '케이크와 함께 우유를 마셔요.
