        (19, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '의사선생님의 말씀을 떠올린 토비는 전화를 걸려고 해요.', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/image/hospital/story01/011.png', 'NORMAL', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/voice/hospital/story01/11.mp3', 2),
        (20, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '토비는 어디로 전화를 걸어야 할까요?', '', 'QUIZ', 'https://tobycarrotbucket.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/assets/voice/hospital/story01/12.mp3', 2),
        (21, '2024-03-27 17:36:11.000000', '2024-03-27 17:36:12.000000', '토비가 재빨리 119에 신고해 코코는 금방 나을 수 있었어요.
